  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단상자, 패키지, 박스 생산</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28e7c20f-f11c-4941-804f-8d1dde1ed4c6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-464501a5-37bf-4a1f-9ccb-5e43ab64892a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045728673/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">소량과 대량의 수량 기준</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>모든 인쇄물이 그렇지만 대량생산으로 진행해야만 인쇄물의 단가를 맞출 수 있습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a616a8a-379e-4a9f-b7ed-7880e2fce076\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4759f343-7fbc-48e0-81b3-32bfcde800dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1c0e63c-43b4-48cc-8bd1-568839010990\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f4b1813-67f6-4d1c-95e6-8d1e0337f395\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만약 카탈로그 1,000부의 단가가 10,000,000원이라면 10부로 소량 제작하면 10,000원으로 제작할 수는 없다는 뜻일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-921ad1ff-8d94-435f-9da0-630fdb6db0d4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0b68384-a5bb-4b94-a4e8-14976a00745c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e2ad4b4c-5e80-4784-a8a3-5bf9e150b6ef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-237e4694-7d87-4bac-a549-92751baa8afe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지도 100개의 @개당 단가가 100,000원이라면 5,000개로 수량을 늘리면 5,000,000원으로 견적이 나오지 않는 이유입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bcafd89a-b772-456f-8e5f-57b11b760753\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-afb89a82-c25a-4a5e-bf21-34e805c9ceb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7002bee8-4aeb-4f73-b1d5-a1d92825b7bc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8b3eddc4-15ad-4c9e-8cc9-d87ef8936ffd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량이 많을수록 단가는 낮아지게 되어 있습니다. 하지만 도대체 몇 개를 해야 소량 디지털 인쇄와 대량 오프셋 인쇄의 단가 경계가 무너질까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db8046ed-435b-4995-ab87-dd1cbb76f8ff\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045728673/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74f0b1ce-2103-4144-86df-4f72cbcb404d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8979ee8-82ac-4e0f-bc21-cf74a4753d56\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3e8ba275-977c-43c7-bfa9-27b92826f299\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>통상의 경우 200개라고 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aec59a54-0016-4bb8-b73d-150d9162e592\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fb5dc11c-ff92-4371-85bb-c1669c0b3f3f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9176946-fae2-4a01-b6f4-a4023a046443\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b33c61e5-d90f-4ed8-a455-c16055087fb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">200부 카탈로그가 넘어가면 오프셋으로 제작하는 것이 더 저렴해질 수 있습니다. 물론 사이즈에 따라 달라질 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ecb399c5-9a13-4c83-814b-e2c75f1c4814\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-36ec79f9-7b0a-47f1-9054-7b2884ed3d83\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d6688b8-9fe5-4f79-9326-311ec8714909\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25795282-9efc-4689-9b9f-bdb5186e7650\" style=\"color:#555555;\">패키지는 사이즈에 영향을 많이 받기 때문에 수량이 다르지만 100개 미만이 소량으로 취급받습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fa60330-0289-4f72-8d50-7c1cc3f45fdd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e52c7205-9d97-4360-9964-619c3a5c3d02\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91e04a8e-a404-4d42-9bb9-451eba424d58\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd790039-ca84-4ab7-8b82-85de6f3f534d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 여러분이 패키지 전문 업체에 전화를 해서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-44b92de8-0703-48ce-ade0-13fd7d4ff19d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>\"대량 400개를 주문할게요!\"라고</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5fab2bd7-d254-4ac2-a6e0-e582ba04b9aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 말하면 패키지 업체 입장에서는 소량이라고 말할 겁니다. 또는 그 수량을 취급하지 않는다고 이야기할지도 모릅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-05bb3fc2-2f92-4bea-8afc-3f1a98c85bd5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-57c09779-a5d9-4084-96cb-7780750bc851\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc79d722-a502-47b6-b875-e062ba2d2777\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-095cd0c9-1ac0-4193-89af-f94db7b1098c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">단상자는 그렇다고 치고 싸바리 박스의 경우는 더 심합니다. 싸바리 박스는 단상자나 합지 박스에 비해 소량 제작이 거의 불가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4e3735c-af43-4e21-9c3e-88ee9ebb70a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-833799d8-7fe8-462f-9f39-f5f953e444d8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0927ce3c-2afe-47c2-8e17-ac2f6a0a2dde\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ff24715b-b82d-40d3-b923-d48b2868d431\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러므로 싸바리 박스를 촬영용이나 지원금 샘플 제출용 또는 시험검사를 위한 제출, 심지어는 본 작업 전에 샘플 인쇄 등으로 문의를 많이 주십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-20502bda-e5b7-4607-bd34-568d8708e22b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045728673/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b56f1ee8-8244-4356-a85e-ab58f25c11ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9cb856d3-adcb-40ab-98ed-22ebb85facac\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e374130-d7a5-4ac1-b72b-671e30130317\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cb2c1c1a-20c3-47a5-9774-681c090585d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc967e3e-5eb1-4740-af1e-193f4c9dd2db\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇다면 싸바리 박스 샘플 2개를 의뢰한다면 가능하거나 금액은 어떨까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-50982992-daa1-44fd-a0a4-a3896a11eb8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045728673/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37ada11e-797a-435b-b751-2def0812fb20\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5ad14c03-1e7d-4c4f-94ea-2675fdf16568\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b3519a2-fe36-442b-8d60-5a193d200d22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-62f9be2f-2b42-41c7-aff0-936f28a8494c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그전에 소량과 대량 인쇄의 방법에 대해 잠깐 설명합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6c0be4d-70b5-42b0-bb80-ae87cc3c56e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a2a93689-90b3-42ba-988e-6faf712388ab\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f75bb33f-065a-4de3-9fe5-697b7597eb80\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224045728673/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-16868c35-35b3-4aaa-8bd0-90335830b154\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-cad855aa-8fc0-498b-a61c-905a8facdb21\" style=\"\">제미나이 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ffd571c-9da5-4109-8048-0ed6c98ec96e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59329af8-edf9-4d2f-8843-8051fab66c37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6c67962-67e2-4783-944c-7157edafa9c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량과 대량은 일단 인쇄 방식이 다릅니다. 인디고 기계를 필두로 사이즈 2절까지 디지털 인쇄가 2020년 후반부터 활성화되기 시작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-daa1bc42-c507-4fcb-a974-bd6306fc9a24\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c8bf133c-a5fd-4e4a-ae09-d0540d42b18e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d4458ef9-dc1f-4ef3-8fe4-983161dd728c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3037951e-0930-4ef1-9a9c-02ab53f9f828\" style=\"color:#555555;\">출력을 하지 않고 낱장으로 직접 인쇄를 하기 때문에 CTP(Computer To Plate)에 출력해서 시범 인쇄를 하고 핀을 맞추고 색상을 PQC로 조절해 가면서 인쇄하는 오프셋 인쇄 방식에 비해 장당 단가가 저렴하고 품질의 퀄리티도 높아졌다고 볼 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18f081f0-d2bf-417d-b350-8fd298b411f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f430a6f6-68a0-498a-b268-14d3847f2596\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c0f356c9-8b84-40db-a805-3fadf8c45902\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bcb57b68-c65b-42fc-8560-88c2d7ba5138\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://www.hp.com/kr-ko/industrial-printers/indigo-digital-presses.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hp.com/kr-ko/industrial-printers/indigo-digital-presses.html</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-937ea91c-0893-49c2-88f7-12c9d1781781\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de1de029-cc6a-4e13-b7cc-6f5c6b7dec79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f7253be3-15f1-469f-81dd-ab36e74a889b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 링크는 대표적인 디지털 기계인 인디고 프레스의 HP 사이트입니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10d47b5a-967b-4741-a2b2-99e57b5f9991\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a0d567f-054c-400d-96bf-892ac6076dce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6fd1fa80-2a42-420d-9cf8-953ce88a80d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a4df7b44-6b2d-4f5d-ba87-879318365a63\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>위의 설명처럼 인쇄 방식의 차이가 소량과 대량 생산의 기준이 됩니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8c43856-42c4-4179-a502-e6ae88915868\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a72f272e-74f4-42d1-a25a-c1b39bc98915\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-041b3c69-2075-4755-b651-a7995ddf4a6d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2e6af6de-56cd-4e42-9758-221cac1d3347\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28bd0568-8837-4788-8b2e-8fda8bb7ab1d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecfae16d-45b0-495c-85b2-b26e37ba9d53\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량과 대량의 기준에서 또 하나 중요한 것은 인쇄 외에 커팅의 차이입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a04a208f-e3f8-4f46-bbc8-e65098315aa3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65370f5c-b09d-4b82-a1d8-d70514de3bf0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56372d9f-896b-4357-bf22-06bd2cfc9cc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58619e1a-41a2-4c1b-90dc-cd02d7e6797f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수량이 많은 경우는 목형을 만들고 톰슨(도무송)작업을 하여 외곽 모양을 따냅니다. 이런 경우 목형비와 도무송 비용이 기본적으로 소요되기 때문에 1장을 따내도 이 비용을 지불해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f6ff68a-7eff-481d-8114-d6ac23047c7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-90d88e52-3ea8-40de-8950-06356ffba44c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e71a91a4-d4a9-44c2-984a-418a25bd4d05\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49a7b005-84d4-4daa-934f-1e31dcd4c060\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 불가능을 디지털 커팅 기계가 요 근래는 대체하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-04558867-4006-484e-806e-a83c902f328b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-28265ec8-dcb1-4d52-b497-8513ddd86511\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 디지털 커팅기는 칼선이 모양을 따라가면서 커팅 하게 되기 때문에 속도가 느리고 커팅이 도무송처럼 정교하지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e91ca8e-7b3a-41c5-a51a-0959fb306f8b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8d1a47ac-c96d-4eec-98ee-38ff482a936a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd2bcb3b-2142-47ff-8b00-b674d29e0dc1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bfefc6ed-691d-46dc-befe-27945630baf7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 1장에서부터 자유롭게 커팅 할 수 있기 때문에 단가를 저렴하게 커팅 할 수 있는 유일한 대안입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-e7e776b0-e00a-4431-86d1-5060265cdbea\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1e505cf7-9c03-4f5f-9253-ddf215e747f3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f4797b37-6cb1-46b5-b19e-42eb5ab30665\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>2개 주문 소량 제작 비용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92e3c764-ae53-4717-816e-2606f8ab2b6b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-73ab813e-9816-4c5f-80d2-7cff173f41b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f70f85d-ae45-40d3-8afb-71176df301f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-47c8d7fb-f52c-42af-b407-4b6f1c7abcd9\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>단상자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-542bcadf-4bf0-4f70-879c-d66048ef5ffe\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2e4c8cc6-9b19-4fdc-959f-71ddfbf318de\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-faa94619-4272-40b7-8205-da25139b906d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3ab84048-7a2b-4c0c-8268-7881a80916d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>A3 이만 사이즈일 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2fdf6b1-b72a-4254-aa7b-31cadeca71a8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c6a5bcd-3e36-4a4e-844b-ff8381dc2db4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이비 + 인쇄비 + 코팅비 + 커팅비 + 접착비 + 배송비 모두 포함</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5dfd808e-552b-429f-b41d-a632e1605856\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d1f7cbf7-e379-44ea-b4c5-ff63f3945230\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b6dc7f5e-1c8a-48c3-86c5-f8cde2fb68a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97ec5591-0c70-4d68-9200-567ff487ac41\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">제외 조건</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab60e797-bd4c-472c-b538-803b1792308b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a94faa4c-2e41-492a-8002-6e1d06617655\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a92f1b96-54f7-406d-8eef-b6f7698816f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c21b8de4-99a1-4463-8cdf-1a9918e65470\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 사이즈가 큰 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-768239df-4d57-4957-9299-cae978ae2c3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53e79fb0-45db-44ff-9b7c-04f6628a8455\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 종이를 특별하게 요구하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-521fc5ed-e549-45a5-80a6-d7f0d96e361f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a4890eb-1c84-4aeb-a5e2-5fc2781c4c6d\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 별색인쇄를 요청하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e542cd2-0cf3-426e-a263-c0f91749fc84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e22e97d8-436a-45ae-901f-c6e7a3ffddb3\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 홀로그램 코팅이나 박인쇄, 형압 등 후공정이 있는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-524e640b-e588-4cba-a41a-e6593cbaced0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eff8ba8f-63d7-423c-9be2-24bb526f8211\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 단상자 모양이 일반적이지 않고 커스텀으로 복잡하게 디자인된 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c949f51b-c1e5-4645-b19d-17289218794e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b128cd44-3546-44a2-a21a-6152d8e434ac\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 납기가 당일 출고를 원할 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"