id=\"SE-e7551447-cb34-498e-a4d9-ee5f026dd892\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6339ac8-f789-44a6-8220-375f0a71435b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">골판지 합지 박스부터는 소량이 거의 제작 불가로 보시면 됩니다. 하지만 촬영용이나 시험인쇄 또는 지원 사업 제출용의 경우 샘플로 2개 정도 제작하시는 경우가 있습니다. 이런 경우 반드시 상담을 통해 진행하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-23097691-c124-4859-a841-760ea16644e5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-41fa3aa3-cf0d-4638-ba3b-90000ee10457\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5fb1dfe2-ea2e-4e28-b999-91c29fb2bdc5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fe071b01-2c54-4824-b9b0-cd820a3b9ac7\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>싸바리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36ffe5b4-72ec-41ba-b7ba-e56e07e41410\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-455aaec8-798b-4e02-9cf0-213130489e09\" style=\"color:#36851e;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7594e3f5-34cb-4c45-8cb4-2759d4e77718\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-75000bff-e8d9-4bfb-b2e5-13479b364f74\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>일반 싸바리 박스의 경우</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-325e62fc-c802-4179-ac31-a91cc4f1896a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ef248119-f1cc-4ec1-9151-a6370739bd0d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이비 + 갱판지 비용 + 인쇄비 + 코팅비 + 목형비 + 도무송비 + 접착비 + 배송비 모두 포함</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9030fcd2-cce3-4e9b-bb7b-48d055eb6d83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aff96951-0dd1-4bb3-8c9a-c7a98c93a919\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f8099207-24d1-4ad9-8e41-314ea70b8699\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8127d45c-e226-43f6-8c78-5ae9a69e32de\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">제외 조건 : 추가 비용이 발생합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-85c34ade-b5cf-454f-a341-70c17bc3167b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1de05dde-cde7-4ae4-a753-714afb5a426e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a7927d03-abaf-4fa6-b364-8d49630c70db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba5571ea-d454-4d8e-b5e3-589fb2bbc03e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 일반적인 형태나 조건이 아닌 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28dd31bf-b7b1-4a88-a28a-98edca3a2f84\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-950e552a-7431-484c-9fc9-f60ac1b1e617\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 사이즈가 큰 경우나 자석의 경우는 비용이 추가됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45c31896-01c9-4b44-b21b-940ca44d2809\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-49b67f11-83e8-4aca-bbba-721e40b5bf03\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 종이를 특별하게 요구하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bceab475-c359-4788-bc58-83c755d49079\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9424ee88-2fed-4075-a85b-7dea80644d58\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 별색인쇄, 실크인쇄를 요청하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bbe8bfe-3e76-4a7f-8034-3d3be6e85d4c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0e4c490f-5964-4f5d-b88d-e9fec18c6131\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 홀로그램 코팅이나 박인쇄, 형압 등 후공정이 있는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc18e3f1-c856-4e78-830a-4a1b37d457c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-47b3f566-a511-427b-8ec7-c3caddd74ce7\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 싸바리 박스의 칼선이 일반적이지 않고 커스텀으로 복잡하게 디자인된 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd109855-90c8-4a3d-9dcf-b0bc8880d018\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9a8aaa46-47e1-4799-9d15-6ad98d9245e1\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">· 납기를 빠르게 요청하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e29d2b4b-c84e-4532-8084-75e31713e319\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0061044-d6fa-4f6f-8ad0-7ed6684c9781\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c98c6681-2ffc-4d11-bb5c-45fbc5c7417f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-291fdf1d-d4af-4856-bc70-dcf4b6961b15\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>약 500,000원부터 ~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed965faf-aae0-45cc-b3fb-c142330c9f4b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-849897cb-d068-43de-b249-878c1526071d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76b31c6c-c304-47f2-863e-ca93d338e3d8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b0a45026-5ac6-4ae9-a975-4c4eea2d3973\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">싸바리는 최소비용이 50만원에서 출발합니다. 통상 샘플을 만드는데도 인쇄와 후공정까지 하면 100만원이 넘어가는 경우가 대부분입니다. 반드시 상담 후 진행하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48ce8a53-03b7-4f65-9d54-6e237a0add83\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e776c727-d8ec-416c-b759-39043909c760\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}